data.comment: The match is underway at Strandvallen.
Ostersund are whistled for offside.
In the minute 2, Can Mjallby capitalize from this throw-in deep inside Ostersund's half?
Jacob Bergstrom's header is off-target for Mjallby.
Kaspar Sjoberg awards Ostersund a goal kick.
In the minute 3, Throw-in for Mjallby at Strandvallen.
Throw-in for Mjallby in their own half.
Mjallby have been given a penalty...
In the minute 5, Moses Ogbu converts the penalty to give Mjallby a 1-0 lead.
Kaspar Sjoberg signals a free kick to Ostersund in their own half.
Mjallby push upfield and Jacob Bergstrom gets his head to the ball. The attempt is cleared by an alert Ostersund defence.
In the minute 8, Can Ostersund get the ball into an attacking position from this throw-in in Mjallby's half?
Joel Nilsson of Mjallby smashes in a shot on target. The keeper saves, though.
Throw-in for Mjallby in the half of Ostersund.
In the minute 9, A throw-in for the home team on the opposite half.
Corner awarded to Mjallby.
Kaspar Sjoberg signals a throw-in for Mjallby, close to Ostersund's area.
In the minute 11, Mjallby have been awarded a corner by Kaspar Sjoberg.
Mjallby's Kadir Hodzic goes close with his head but his effort is blocked.
It's a goal kick for the home team in Hallevik.
In the minute 13, Throw-in Ostersund.
Ball safe as Ostersund is awarded a throw-in in their half.
Mjallby take a comfortable 2-0 lead thanks to Jacob Bergstrom.
In the minute 15, That's a fine assist from David Lofquist.
Kaspar Sjoberg signals a free kick to Ostersund.
Ostersund to take a throw-in in Mjallby territory.
In the minute 17, Kaspar Sjoberg signals a Ostersund throw-in in Mjallby's half.
Kaspar Sjoberg awards the home team a throw-in.
Mjallby awarded a throw-in in their own half.
In the minute 22, Kaspar Sjoberg awards the away team a throw-in.
Mjallby to take a throw-in in Ostersund territory.
Mjallby's Moses Ogbu gets in a shot on goal at Strandvallen. But the effort is unsuccessful.
In the minute 24, Mjallby are coming forward and Joel Nilsson gets in a strike, it misses the target, however.
Ostersund have a goal kick.
Kaspar Sjoberg signals a Mjallby throw-in in Ostersund's half.
In the minute 24, Throw-in Ostersund.
Goal! Mjallby extend their lead to 3-0 through Moses Ogbu.
Joel Nilsson instrumental with a fine assist.
In the minute 29, Can Ostersund get the ball into an attacking position from this throw-in in Mjallby's half?
Mjallby awarded a throw-in in their own half.
Ostersund have been awarded a corner by Kaspar Sjoberg.
In the minute 30, Ludvig Fritzson (Ostersund) is given an opening but the shot is blocked by a defender.
Mjallby awarded a free kick in their own half.
Francis Jno-Baptiste (Ostersund) has been booked and must now be careful not to get a second yellow card.
In the minute 33, In Hallevik a free kick has been awarded the home team.
Free kick for Ostersund in their own half.
Ball goes out of play for a Mjallby goal kick.
In the minute 35, Throw-in for Mjallby in the half of Ostersund.
In Hallevik Mjallby attack through Jesper Lofgren. The finish is off target, however.
Goal kick for Ostersund at Strandvallen.
In the minute 36, Kaspar Sjoberg signals a free kick to Ostersund in their own half.
Kaspar Sjoberg awards Ostersund a goal kick.
Ostersund have a goal kick.
In the minute 40, Free kick for Mjallby in the half of Ostersund.
Mjallby pushes forward through David Lofquist, whose finish on goal is saved.
Amir Azrafshan is making the team's first substitution at Strandvallen with Marco Weymans replacing Kalpi Ouattara.
In the minute 41, Mjallby have a dangerous throw-in.
Throw-in for Mjallby in their own half.
A throw-in for the home team on the opposite half.
In the minute 45, 1 minutes of injury time will be added to the 1st half.
It's a goal kick for the away team in Hallevik.
The first-half is over at Strandvallen.
In the minute 46, Kaspar Sjoberg has blown to start the second-half.
Corner awarded to Mjallby.
Amir Azrafshan (Ostersund) is making a second substitution, with Jerell Sellars replacing Nebiyou Perry.
In the minute 47, Ostersund awarded a free kick in their own half.
Throw-in high up the field for Mjallby in Hallevik.
Free kick Ostersund.
In the minute 49, Ostersund push forward at Strandvallen and Ronald Mukiibi gets in a strike. This is blocked, however, by a determined Mjallby defence.
In Hallevik Ostersund drive forward through Isak Ssewankambo. His shot is on target but it's saved.
Eirik Haugan (Ostersund) wins the ball in the air but heads wide.
In the minute 50, Ball goes out of play for a Mjallby goal kick.
Throw-in for Ostersund in the half of Mjallby.
Free kick for Ostersund in their own half.
In the minute 53, Mjallby are in shooting range from this free kick.
Marco Weymans (Ostersund) has received a yellow card from Kaspar Sjoberg.
Mjallby's Besard Sabovic misses with an attempt on goal.
In the minute 54, Goal kick for Ostersund at Strandvallen.
A throw-in for the home team on the opposite half.
Mjallby needs to be cautious. Ostersund have an attacking throw-in.
In the minute 55, Can Mjallby get the ball into an attacking position from this throw-in in Ostersund's half?
Ostersund to take a throw-in in Mjallby territory.
Throw-in for Mjallby at Strandvallen.
In the minute 58, Mjallby's Joel Nilsson is on target but unsuccessful.
Moses Ogbu gets his shot on target but fails to score for Mjallby.
In Hallevik, Blair Turgott of Ostersund is presented with a shooting opportunity. But the strike is blocked by the covering defence.
In the minute 59, Ostersund have been awarded a corner by Kaspar Sjoberg.
Corner awarded to Ostersund.
Jerell Sellars (Ostersund) goes for goal but the shot is blocked by an alert defence.
In the minute 60, Free kick for Mjallby in their own half.
Nikolaos Dosis is replacing Charlie Colkett for Ostersund at Strandvallen.
Free kick Ostersund.
In the minute 62, Ball safe as Mjallby is awarded a throw-in in their half.
Joel Nilsson of Mjallby gets in a strike, but is off target.
Kaspar Sjoberg awards Ostersund a goal kick.
In the minute 63, Mjallby awarded a throw-in in their own half.
Free kick for Ostersund in the half of Mjallby.
Kaspar Sjoberg signals a free kick to Mjallby in their own half.
Ostersund have a goal kick.
In the minute 65, At Strandvallen, Nikolaos Dosis has been yellow-carded for the away team.
Goal kick for Mjallby at Strandvallen.
In the minute 66, Throw-in for Ostersund close to the penalty box.
Blair Turgott for Ostersund gets in a strike but fails to hit the target.
Ball goes out of play for a Mjallby goal kick.
In the minute 68, Ostersund are pushing forward but Felix Horberg's finish is wide of the goal.
It's a goal kick for the home team in Hallevik.
Ostersund awarded a free kick in their own half.
In the minute 70, Kaspar Sjoberg signals a free kick to Mjallby in their own half.
Kaspar Sjoberg signals a Mjallby throw-in in Ostersund's half.
Free kick for Ostersund in their own half.
It's a goal kick for the home team in Hallevik.
In the minute 72, Jesper Gustavsson for Mjallby has been booked by Kaspar Sjoberg and receives a first yellow card.
Throw-in high up the field for Ostersund in Hallevik.
In the minute 74, Goal kick for Mjallby at Strandvallen.
Adam Petersson is replacing David Lofquist for the home team.
Marcus Lantz is making the team's second substitution at Strandvallen with Erik Parsson replacing Jacob Bergstrom.
In the minute 75, David Batanero is on a sub for Jesper Gustavsson for Mjallby.
Throw-in for Mjallby in their own half.
Free kick in a good position for Ostersund!
In the minute 77, Ostersund's Nikolaos Dosis gets in a shot but it is blocked by a Mjallby defender.
Ostersund have been awarded a corner by Kaspar Sjoberg.
Corner awarded to Ostersund.
In the minute 78, Kaspar Sjoberg signals a free kick to Mjallby.
In the minute 79, Mjallby drive into the zone and Joel Nilsson is presented with a brilliant opportunity. But his strike hits the upright!
The away team have replaced Francis Jno-Baptiste with Henrik Bellman. This is the fifth substitution made today by Amir Azrafshan.
The away team replace Blair Turgott with Malcolm Stolt.
Mjallby have been awarded a corner by Kaspar Sjoberg.
Important block from the Ostersund defence as Kadir Hodzic fires in a strike for Mjallby.
In the minute 81, Ostersund have a goal kick.
Kaspar Sjoberg signals a Ostersund throw-in in Mjallby's half.
In Hallevik a free kick has been awarded the away team.
In the minute 83, Mamudo Moro is replacing Moses Ogbu for Mjallby at Strandvallen.
Marcus Lantz (Mjallby) is making a fourth substitution, with Martin Spelmann replacing Besard Sabovic.
Corner awarded to Ostersund.
In the minute 85, Kaspar Sjoberg signals a free kick to Mjallby.
Mjallby drive upfield and Mamudo Moro gets in a shot. The strike is blocked by a Ostersund defender.
Free kick Ostersund.
In the minute 86, Mjallby awarded a free kick in their own half.
Free kick for Mjallby in the half of Ostersund.
Throw-in for Mjallby at Strandvallen.
In the minute 88, Ostersund awarded a free kick in their own half.
Free kick for Ostersund in their own half.
The 2nd half is prolonged by 3 minutes of added time.
Ostersund to take a throw-in in Mjallby territory.
That's full-time at Strandvallen. The final score is 3-0.
